{"text_id":217852,"tokens":["In"," the"," quest"," to"," understand"," the"," nature"," of"," dark"," energy",","," relaxed"," galaxy"," clusters"," offer"," a"," promising"," avenue"," for"," investigation"," due"," to"," their"," simple"," internal"," dynamics"," and"," lack"," of"," disturbances","."," In"," this"," work",","," we"," present"," improved"," constraints"," on"," dark"," energy"," derived"," from"," Chandra"," X","-","ray"," observations"," of"," the"," largest"," relaxed"," galaxy"," clusters",".","\n\n","The"," problem"," we"," aim"," to"," solve"," is"," the"," uncertainty"," surrounding"," the"," equation"," of"," state"," of"," dark"," energy",","," which"," is"," a"," key"," parameter"," in"," cosmological"," models","."," The"," motivation"," for"," our"," research"," is"," the"," potential"," of"," galaxy"," clusters"," as"," laboratories"," for"," studying"," the"," properties"," of"," dark"," energy","."," Specifically",","," we"," focus"," on"," the"," use"," of"," X","-","ray"," observations"," to"," measure"," the"," entropy"," of"," the"," intra","cluster"," medium"," (","IC","M",")"," and"," its"," relationship"," with"," cluster"," mass",".","\n\n","Our"," key"," ideas"," and"," methodology"," involve"," the"," use"," of"," hydrostatic"," equilibrium"," and"," the"," entropy"," profile"," of"," the"," ICM"," to"," constrain"," the"," equation"," of"," state"," of"," dark"," energy","."," We"," analyze"," Chandra"," X","-","ray"," observations"," of"," a"," sample"," of"," ","2","5"," relaxed"," galaxy"," clusters",","," spanning"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," masses"," and"," reds","hi","fts","."," By"," modeling"," the"," ICM"," as"," a"," poly","t","ropic"," gas",","," we"," measure"," the"," entropy"," profile"," of"," each"," cluster"," and"," use"," it"," to"," infer"," the"," density"," and"," temperature"," profiles","."," We"," then"," use"," these"," profiles"," to"," estimate"," the"," cluster"," mass"," and"," compare"," it"," to"," the"," mass"," inferred"," from"," weak"," lens","ing"," observations",".","\n\n","Our"," results"," show"," that"," the"," entropy"," profile"," of"," the"," ICM"," is"," a"," powerful"," tool"," for"," con","straining"," the"," equation"," of"," state"," of"," dark"," energy","."," By"," combining"," our"," X","-","ray"," observations"," with"," cosmic"," microwave"," background"," data"," and"," Type"," Ia"," supernova"," data",","," we"," obtain"," improved"," constraints"," on"," the"," equation"," of"," state"," of"," dark"," energy",","," with"," a"," precision"," of"," ","8","%"," at"," the"," ","6","8","%"," confidence"," level","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}